Description: Spamcheck-Python
        ================
        
        A simple Python wrapper for `Postmark’s Spamcheck API`_
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            $ pip install spamcheck
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: python
        
            import spamcheck
        
            result = spamcheck.check(your_email_content, report=True)
            score = result['score']
            report = result['report']
        
